OL,3,CApple at 50: How a garage start-up
OL,4,Cbecame a #3 trillion tech giant
OL,6,FWords by Producer Lois Smith
OL,8,FApple Inc is one of the most
OL,9,Frecognisable brands in the world, and
OL,10,Fas it marks its 50th anniversary, its
OL,11,Finfluence on the world shows no signs
OL,12,Fof fading.
OL,14,FFounded on April 1, 1976, the tech
OL,15,Fgiant has helped shape not just
OL,16,Fpersonal computing, but modern culture
OL,17,Fitself, transforming how people
OL,18,Fcommunicate, work, and consume media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
