FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31002
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1775067061
OL,3,CApple at 50: How a garage start-up
OL,4,Cbecame a #3 trillion tech giant
OL,6,FToday, its reach is vast: government
OL,7,Fdata published last year suggests that
OL,8,F55% of UK smartphone users own an
OL,9,FiPhone. So if you're reading this on
OL,10,Fyour phone, there's a strong chance it
OL,11,Fwas made by Apple.
OL,13,FFrom Steve Jobs hand-building its
OL,14,Ffirst computer in the basement of his
OL,15,Fparents' home, Apple is estimated to
OL,16,Fbe worth $3.73 trillion (#3 trillion)
OL,17,Ftoday.
OL,19,FITV News breaks down Apple's
OL,20,Finventions, influence, and internal
OL,21,Fstruggles of the last five decades.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
